One of our main focuses it to provided real time data to our potential users (university students) in order to provide value for our product. 
Some solutions we have come up with and need to develop further are: Motion Sensors
                                                                     Pressure Sensors
                                                                     Facial Recognition Cameras
                                                                     
Any solution we choose, we will need to manufacture a proto-type and link that to our user-interface system (app).
